        <content><![CDATA[<p>It is possible to make element settings editable in the form-based content editor instead of accessing the settings via the gear wheel <img style="width: 14px;" title="propertyIconActive" src="%(link0)" alt="" /> in the page editor. In order to do so, the developer has to check the option "Show element settings in content editor" in the first tab of a formatter configuration.</p>]]></content>
